<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 18:08:02 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>内塔尼亚胡试图推迟以色列国防军调查，以色列国家审计长开始审查军队在加沙战争中的行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/as-netanyahu-tries-to-delay-idf-probe-state-watchdog-begins-review-of-armys-gaza-conduct/0000018c-dfc6-daf6-a5df-dffe871c0000</link><description>国家审计长马塔尼亚胡·恩格尔曼通知总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡政府，他将于本周开始审查与战争有关的一系列问题</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 17:49:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/as-netanyahu-tries-to-delay-idf-probe-state-watchdog-begins-review-of-armys-gaza-conduct/0000018c-dfc6-daf6-a5df-dffe871c0000</guid></item><item><title>联合国人道主义事务负责人表示，“不适合居住”的加沙地带“饥荒即将来临”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-06/ty-article/un-humanitarian-chief-says-famine-around-the-corner-in-uninhabitable-gaza/0000018c-df45-daf6-a5df-df7dfb880000</link><description>马丁·格里菲斯还警告说，一场迫在眉睫的公共卫生灾难称，加沙为数不多的几家部分运转的医院已经不堪重负，物资严重短缺，而医疗设施遭到无情攻击，传染病正在蔓延，</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 15:33:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-06/ty-article/un-humanitarian-chief-says-famine-around-the-corner-in-uninhabitable-gaza/0000018c-df45-daf6-a5df-df7dfb880000</guid></item><item><title>真主党向以色列发射大型火箭弹，作为对哈马斯领导人被杀的“初步回应”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-fires-large-rocket-salvo-in-initial-response-to-killing-of-hamas-leader/0000018c-df37-d751-ad8d-ffb7ff5a0000</link><description>空中渗透和火箭警报整个周六持续不断，以色列军队表示拦截了几个可疑目标，并使天露探测和警告气球重新投入运行。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 15:29:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-fires-large-rocket-salvo-in-initial-response-to-killing-of-hamas-leader/0000018c-df37-d751-ad8d-ffb7ff5a0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日，以色列国防军坦克在贝埃里家中丧生的以色列人家属要求调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israelis-killed-in-beeri-home-hit-by-tank-fire-on-october-7-demand-probe/0000018c-de77-daf6-a5df-df7f22d60000</link><description>家属表示，对这一事件的调查必须立即展开，而不是在战争结束后展开。该事件是哈马斯关押在贝埃里一所房屋内的以色列人在与以色列国防军坦克交火中丧生的事件。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 12:24:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israelis-killed-in-beeri-home-hit-by-tank-fire-on-october-7-demand-probe/0000018c-de77-daf6-a5df-df7f22d60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列部长的诽谤危及我们的安全——并呼吁采取施压行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ministers-mudslinging-imperils-our-security-and-calls-for-a-pressure-campaign/0000018c-ddd1-daf6-a5df-dffd56780000</link><description>周五安全内阁会议上的惨败，右翼部长们对以色列国防军对其 10 月 7 日失误进行的内部调查进行了猛烈抨击，这是即将发生的事情的令人作呕的开胃菜</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 09:30:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ministers-mudslinging-imperils-our-security-and-calls-for-a-pressure-campaign/0000018c-ddd1-daf6-a5df-dffd56780000</guid></item><item><title>“当时没有关于如何对待儿童人质的知识，所以我们编造了这个。我们决定不拥抱或问问题”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/there-was-no-info-on-treating-child-hostages-we-made-it-up-we-had-no-room-for-mistakes/0000018c-db93-d751-ad8d-ffb7c7090000</link><description>埃夫拉特·布隆-哈列夫博士和她的工作人员在抵达施耐德儿童医疗中心后立即接收了从哈马斯囚禁中解救出来的年轻人质，没有先例，没有固定的程序等待着他们。没有犯错的余地</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 05:23:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/there-was-no-info-on-treating-child-hostages-we-made-it-up-we-had-no-room-for-mistakes/0000018c-db93-d751-ad8d-ffb7c7090000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队命名周六在加沙战斗中丧生的士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article-live/idf-strikes-hezbollah-operational-hq-in-lebanon-hostage-families-arrive-in-qatar/0000018c-dc92-d751-ad8d-ffb6524b0000</link><description>真主党声称向上加利利发射火箭弹是对哈马斯领导人在贝鲁特被杀的“初步反应” ■ 以色列国防军袭击了从黎巴嫩发射火箭的小组 ■ 10 月 7 日在贝埃里家中被坦克炮火袭击而丧生的以色列人家属要求以色列国防军进行调查 ■ 在自10月7日以来，以色列境内至少有1,300名平民和士兵被杀；至少 133 名人质在加沙被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙有 22,722 人死亡、58,166 人受伤</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 02:31:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-06/ty-article-live/idf-strikes-hezbollah-operational-hq-in-lebanon-hostage-families-arrive-in-qatar/0000018c-dc92-d751-ad8d-ffb6524b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队中有人决定将这个安静的约旦河西岸地区带入暴力圈</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/someone-in-the-idf-decided-to-bring-this-quiet-west-bank-area-into-the-circle-of-violence/0000018c-daf0-daf6-a5df-dffcc42c0000</link><description>一枚以色列国防军导弹射入约旦河西岸难民营中心，造成六名年轻人死亡，七人受伤。军队最初拒绝救护车进入现场，边防警察对伤员拳打脚踢。几天后，军队再次入侵营地</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 20:01:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/someone-in-the-idf-decided-to-bring-this-quiet-west-bank-area-into-the-circle-of-violence/0000018c-daf0-daf6-a5df-dffcc42c0000</guid></item><item><title>年龄：23​​岁；在以色列停留时间：25天；在加沙被扣为人质的时间：90多天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/age-23-time-in-israel-25-days-time-held-hostage-in-gaza-over-90-days/0000018c-d9c6-daf6-a5df-dffe5c260000</link><description>一连几天，都没有比平术赤的踪影。多亏了以色列国防军发布的加沙希法医院的一段视频，他在尼泊尔的家人才得知他被活着带到加沙。三个月后，他在大屠杀中幸存的朋友们重温了恐怖时刻，并参加了拯救他的活动</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 19:26:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/age-23-time-in-israel-25-days-time-held-hostage-in-gaza-over-90-days/0000018c-d9c6-daf6-a5df-dffe5c260000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的失败主义者是哈马斯有用的白痴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-defeatists-are-hamas-useful-idiots/0000018c-dac9-ddba-abad-dae9a5d40000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 19:25:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-defeatists-are-hamas-useful-idiots/0000018c-dac9-ddba-abad-dae9a5d40000</guid></item><item><title>犹太-阿拉伯伙伴关系正在以色列建立一个年轻的新和平营</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-jewish-arab-partnership-is-building-a-young-new-peace-camp-in-israel/0000018c-daa9-d751-ad8d-ffadd6e00000</link><description>在加沙战争中，“站在一起”组织进展顺利：它拥有 5,000 名缴纳会费的会员，其学生分会的数量增加了一倍，新的犹太人和阿拉伯人团体正在努力保持团结，并为共同生活注入希望在以色列</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 18:32:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-jewish-arab-partnership-is-building-a-young-new-peace-camp-in-israel/0000018c-daa9-d751-ad8d-ffadd6e00000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗官员试图将致命爆炸归咎于以色列和美国——即使伊斯兰国声称对此负责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/iran-pins-deadly-blasts-on-israel-and-u-s-despite-isis-claiming-responsibility/0000018c-dab5-ddba-abad-dab533f60000</link><description>伊朗指挥官表示，“他们只能充当美国政治和犹太复国主义的代理人和雇佣兵”，革命卫队发誓要对周三造成数十人死亡的自杀式爆炸袭击进行报复</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 18:17:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/iran-pins-deadly-blasts-on-israel-and-u-s-despite-isis-claiming-responsibility/0000018c-dab5-ddba-abad-dab533f60000</guid></item><item><title>为什么中国在以色列-哈马斯战争中站在巴勒斯坦一边</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/why-china-is-siding-with-the-palestinians-in-the-israel-hamas-war/0000018c-da8d-ddba-abad-daad516d0000</link><description>中国的信息更多是针对华盛顿而不是耶路撒冷</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 17:25:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/why-china-is-siding-with-the-palestinians-in-the-israel-hamas-war/0000018c-da8d-ddba-abad-daad516d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列胜利的真实形象是绿线两侧的温和</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-real-victory-picture-is-moderation-on-both-sides-of-the-green-line/0000018c-da25-d751-ad8d-ffa510c40000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 16:23:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-real-victory-picture-is-moderation-on-both-sides-of-the-green-line/0000018c-da25-d751-ad8d-ffa510c40000</guid></item><item><title>部长们与以色列陆军参谋长就 10 月 7 日的调查发生冲突后，内塔尼亚胡的政党和甘茨互相指责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-party-gantz-trade-barbs-after-ministers-clash-with-idf-chief-over-oct-7-probe/0000018c-da32-d751-ad8d-ffb60f1e0000</link><description>甘茨在抨击利库德集团和极右翼部长们猛烈抨击以色列国防军 10 月 7 日对军队行为进行的内部调查时表示，“内阁中发生的事情是战争期间出于政治动机的攻击”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 16:11:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-party-gantz-trade-barbs-after-ministers-clash-with-idf-chief-over-oct-7-probe/0000018c-da32-d751-ad8d-ffb60f1e0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦总理致欧盟高级官员：援助加沙防止大规模移民</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-pm-to-senior-eu-officials-aid-gaza-to-prevent-mass-migration/0000018c-d9f8-d751-ad8d-fffc90db0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦官员担心加沙地带日益不适宜居住的灾难性状况将导致大规模逃亡。他们声称以色列打算采取国际医疗举措来减少人口</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 15:27:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-pm-to-senior-eu-officials-aid-gaza-to-prevent-mass-migration/0000018c-d9f8-d751-ad8d-fffc90db0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列中部阿拉伯城市男子遭枪击身亡；北部一女子被发现车内已无生命体征</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/man-fatally-shot-in-arab-city-in-central-israel-woman-found-lifeless-in-car-in-north/0000018c-d957-d751-ad8d-fff732600000</link><description>枪击事件中尚未逮捕任何嫌疑人 ■ 调查该女子死亡原因的警方正在调查可能的性侵犯和谋杀</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 12:14:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/man-fatally-shot-in-arab-city-in-central-israel-woman-found-lifeless-in-car-in-north/0000018c-d957-d751-ad8d-fff732600000</guid></item><item><title>以色列部长们公开反对 10 月 7 日对军队行为进行的内部调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ministers-come-out-against-team-set-to-probe-armys-conduct-on-october-7/0000018c-d91c-ddba-abad-dbbd845b0000</link><description>以色列部长们猛烈抨击陆军参谋长领导对哈马斯袭击失败的调查。 “我们正处于战争之中，而你现在就开始调查？”有人说</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 11:45:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ministers-come-out-against-team-set-to-probe-armys-conduct-on-october-7/0000018c-d91c-ddba-abad-dbbd845b0000</guid></item><item><title>他的基布兹宣布，以色列人质于 10 月 7 日被杀，尸体被扣押在加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostage-killed-on-october-7-body-being-held-in-gaza-his-kibbutz-announces/0000018c-d8ea-d751-ad8d-ffee89ab0000</link><description>塔米尔·阿达尔 (Tamir Adar) 是亚法·阿达尔 (Yaffa Adar) 的孙子，亚法·阿达尔 (Yaffa Adar) 也曾在加沙被哈马斯扣押，并通过人质交易获释。战争爆发以来，加沙132名人质中的26名人质已确认死亡</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 10:04:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostage-killed-on-october-7-body-being-held-in-gaza-his-kibbutz-announces/0000018c-d8ea-d751-ad8d-ffee89ab0000</guid></item><item><title>随着反对以色列民主的政变停止，推翻内塔尼亚胡的战斗即将来临</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/we-are-well-into-the-day-before-israels-war-in-gaza-ends/0000018c-d626-d751-ad8d-ffa636ef0000</link><description>这位首相的毒药机器在10月7日之后沉寂了几天，现在在他试图保住职位时又恢复了全速运转。他的司法部长亚里夫·莱文（Yariv Levin）仍在继续他的谎言、半真半假和煽动行为</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 04:00:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/we-are-well-into-the-day-before-israels-war-in-gaza-ends/0000018c-d626-d751-ad8d-ffa636ef0000</guid></item></channel></rss>